Description:
  A Yeoman generator for Bespoke.js presentations

Example:
  yo bespoke

  This will create:
    ├── .editorconfig                 : Config for editor like VIM...
    ├── .gitignore                    : Classic gitignore
    ├── gulpfile.js                   : Gulp build script
    ├── package.json                  : Node dependencies
    ├── Gemfile                       : Ruby dependencies (only used in AsciiDoc-based presentations)
    ├── README.adoc                   : "How to" documentation
    ├── node_modules/**               : All the installed Node modules
    └── src
        ├── images
        │   └── bespoke-logo.jpg      : Sample image
        ├── index.(pug | adoc | html) : Slide content
        ├── scripts
        │   └── main.js               : Bespoke configuration
        └── styles
            ├── base.styl             : Base stylesheet
            ├── main.styl             : Aggregate stylesheet
            └── user.styl             : User stylesheet
